two lines of the  jakarta monorail  are under construction the green line serving  semanggi casablanca road kuningan  semanggi  and the blue line serving  kampung melayu casablanca road tanah abang  roxy  in addition there are plans for a twoline subway mrt system with a northsouth line between kota and lebak bulus with connections to both monorail lines and an eastwest line which will connect with the northsouth line at the sawah besar station  the current project which began in 2005 has been halted due to a lack of funds and its future remains uncertain
